title: Proposal for a Harmony Farm & Syrup Pool
body:
# PancakeSwap Welcomes Harmony to Syrup Pool!


CAKE holders, today we are happy to be able to offer you a new Syrup Pool from Harmony, a fast and secure blockchain for decentralized applications.


# The Syrup Pool:
Stake CAKE tokens to earn ONE tokens!

- **Total Tokens:** 5,200,000 ONE
- **Distribution duration:** 60 days
- **Start block:** 8972400 (approx. 9am UTC on July 8th)
- **Finish block:** 10700400 (approx. 9am UTC on September 6th)
- **Token rewards per block:** 3.0092 ONE


## Max Stake per wallet: 
100 CAKE for the first 48 hours, then unlimited CAKE staking afterwards. 

To give as many CAKE holders the opportunity to Farm some juicy pool rewards at a high APY, we will have a 100 CAKE token cap staking limit per user for the first 48 hours.


# The Farm:
In order to host the ONE Syrup Pool, we will need to provide a ONE-BNB farm that will have 2x CAKE rewards for the first 48 hours and then 1x CAKE rewards after that. 


# What is Harmony?

[**Harmony**](https://www.harmony.one/) is your open platform for assets, collectibles, identity, governance. We are an open and fast blockchain.

Harmony mainnet runs Ethereum and Binance Smart Chain applications with 2-second transaction finality and 1000 times lower fees. Harmony’s secure bridges offer cross-chain asset transfers with Ethereum, Binance and other chains.

Build on Harmony, run on all chains. Be the ONE to bridge to all blockchains.


### To learn more about Harmony, the chefs advise you to visit their official communication channels:

- **Website:** [https://www.harmony.one/](https://www.harmony.one/)
- **Twitter:** [https://harmony.one/twitter](https://harmony.one/twitter)
- **Telegram:** [https://harmony.one/telegram](https://harmony.one/telegram)
- **Discord:** [https://harmony.one/discord](https://harmony.one/discord)


# How do you stake CAKE to earn ONE rewards?
If you own CAKE tokens, congratulations! You’re the master of your … pancakes.
Time to step up your taste buds by learning how to stake CAKE with Syrup Pool.

- Visit this webpage: [**https://pancakeswap.finance/syrup** ](https://pancakeswap.finance/syrup )
- Click “Approve CAKE” on the ONE Syrup Pool 
- Click on the stake button.
- Confirm the transaction.

BEP20 ONE will also be circulating and transferable on BSC when we start the Syrup pool, so you will be able to harvest your ONE tokens and trade on PancakeSwap at any time!



# BEWARE OF FOOD POISONING! ⚠️⚠️⚠️💀

**The official ONE token contract address on Binance Smart Chain is:**
[https://www.bscscan.com/address/0x03fF0ff224f904be3118461335064bB48Df47938](https://www.bscscan.com/address/0x03fF0ff224f904be3118461335064bB48Df47938)

Any other ONE token will be a scam and will result in a financial loss for users. Do not buy tokens from any other token address. Always verify the token address before purchasing tokens. If you receive airdrops from another address for ONE tokens, they will be rotten tokens (but not the cool kind!), and we advise you to ignore them.
